cs.IT, cs.OC, cs.CR, cs.PH, cs.NI

The paper discusses the development of a key distribution system over optical channels, which involves information theory (cs.IT), optical communication (cs.OC), cryptography (cs.CR), photonics (cs.PH), and network security (cs.NI). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.IT, cs.OC, and cs.CR, followed by cs.PH and cs.NI.
